      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your training has imbued you with grace and precision when executing maneuvers in weightless environments. When in zero gravity, you move your full land speed when pushing off objects, and you can move along surfaces with handholds as if you had a climb speed equal to your land speed. You also gain a +2 insight bonus to Acrobatics or Athletics checks to avoid becoming @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.QnGpBSHSTiszjPSb]{Off-Kilter} in zero-g.</p>"
